      <c01 level="series">
        <did>
          <unittitle>Topical Files</unittitle>
        </did>
        <scopecontent>
          <p>The Topical Files series consists of five folders. These folders document the activities of the Interfraternity Council (IFC), Interfraternity Alumni Assembly and the Office of the Dean of Men. The IFC folder contains correspondence with the Counselor to Fraternities, statements about the purpose of the IFC, fraternity scholarship reports, and IFC regulations. The Interfraternity Alumni Assembly folder contains the 1926 and 1927 constitution and bylaws of the assembly and scattered minutes.</p>
